  "title": "Buyer (Up to $3500 / 5 days / Changi)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Buyer (ID3575)<br />Location: Changi<br />Working Hours: Mon – Fri 7 Am To 4:30pm<br />Salary: $3500<br /><br />Job Description:<br />• Tactical/ Strategic Purchasing (Sourcing, negotiating, placing order, follow up deliveries, etc)<br />• Vendor Management handling the local & overseas suppliers<br />• Manage on-time delivery program, expediting delivery of materials to meet production requirement, handle supplier shipment discrepancies<br />• Update daily and monthly planning & purchasing reports, follow up weekly with suppliers on forecasted requirements<br />• Generating purchasing order, expediting, re-scheduling, and handling excess and inventory control management<br />• Deal with internal company to support RFQ & buy on behalf if needed.<br />• Ensure timely delivery materials to support the plant’s operation and manufacturing needs<br />• RMA management<br />• Perform other related ad hoc duties assigned to support Purchasing Department<br /><br />Requirements:<br />• Minimum Diploma qualification or other relevant certificates<br />• Minimum 2 year experience in manufacturing/contract manufacturing<br />• Knowledge of Procurement & supply Chain Priciples<br />• Proficiency in Excel, ERP Systems (Epicor)<br />• Good communication, negotiation, Self-motivated and highly responsible with the ability to work under pressure<br />• Knowledge in raw materials & OEM is a must</p>",
